File: plugins/figma/src/figma-api.ts

The bug is on lines 218-219:
```
const retryAfter = response.headers.get('Retry-After');
const retryMs = retryAfter ? Number(retryAfter) * 1000 : undefined;
```

Replace with:
```
const retryAfter = response.headers.get('Retry-After');
const retryMs = retryAfter !== null ? parseRetryAfterMs(retryAfter) : undefined;
```

Add `parseRetryAfterMs` to the existing import from '@opentabs-dev/plugin-sdk' at line 1 (which currently imports `getCookie` and `ToolError`).
